'''Osialfecanakmg''' is an [[acronym]] made up of the chemical symbols of the 8 most abundant [[Chemical element|element]]s in the Earth's [[Crust (geology)|crust]]. Because they are so important, geologists sometimes refer to the elements named below as the '''BIG 8'''.

Element Volume proportions are:

*[[Oxygen]] (O): 46.6%
*[[Silicon]] (Si): 27.7%
*[[Aluminum]] (Al): 8%
*[[Iron]] (Fe): 5%
*[[Calcium]] (Ca): 3.6%
*[[Sodium]] (Na): 2.8%
*[[Potassium]] (K): 2.6%
*[[Magnesium]] (Mg): 2.1%

{{Science mnemonics}}

